# UnicodeTokenizer

UnicodeTokenizer: tokenize all Unicode text, tokenize blank char as a token as default

## ๅ่ฏ่งๅ Tokenize Rules
* ็ฉบ็ฝๅๅ split on blank๏ผ '\n', ' ', '\t'
* ไฟ็ๅณ้ฎ่ฏ keep never_splits
* ่ฅๅฐๅ๏ผๅ่ง่ๅ๏ผๅจ่ง่ฝฌๅ่ง๏ผๅNFD่ง่ๅ๏ผๅๅญ็ฌฆๅๅฒ  nomalize if lower๏ผfull2half๏ผnomalize NFD, then chars split 
    - ็ฑปๅซไธบM๏ผ็ฅ่ฟ ingore if category M ๏ผ category M -> ''
* ๅญ็ฌฆๅๅฒ chars split๏ผ ไปฅๅญ็็ฌฆๅท็ฑปๅซๅ่ฏญ่จๅๅฒ split line by category and languae of characters
    - ๅชๆไธด่ฟๆฐๅญๆ่ฏ only numers joind
    - ๅชๆไธด่ฟๅญๆฏๆ่ฏ only letters joind 
    - ้ซ็็น็ฌๅญ  split high UnicodePoint characters

* ๆชๆญ max_len


## use
> pip install UnicodeTokenizer

```python
